Aning akunum kekebukop ura, Naomi birye el yamal kil ati, “ ‘Anye bira, Yahweh arye weik arye melinamle’ tenen moropne. Nun Ni Koproba Allah arye bico tuba tenesilirye, melisulule. Nun kam unyap ninye babye, akunum dibik ninye babye, tuba tenesilirye, teleb ulisulule. Tonda, an nyapmomnye bira, ara na domsinye Elimelek, el tamnye ulule. Boas bira, Elimelek tamnye ulula ati ara, elce kanye deipsuturye, nun ikin usulul ning ara, melipsutue anya arye, nun ti, ‘Telebe,’ tenepsutop ura, batakana kumce, fia talibuka melipsutue. Na kanye ara elce lyepnamsil ca. Bukni, nunda dina uk unaname,” Naomi birye nyabuk.
